"""
FEPD Files Tab - Forensic Evidence File Explorer
=================================================

Windows "This PC" style forensic file explorer with complete read-only protection.
Shows merged filesystem tree from all evidence images.

Forensic Guarantees:
- 100% read-only access - no modification, deletion, or rename
- All actions logged to Chain of Custody
- Write attempts blocked with clear messaging
- Complete path synchronization with FEPD Terminal

Features:
- Tree view of all evidence filesystems (Disk0, Disk1, etc.)
- User profile detection (👤 Administrator, 👤 Victim, etc.)
- Details panel with SHA-256, timestamps, partition info
- Right-click menu: Open, Hex View, Strings, Export, Hash
- Breadcrumb navigation synced with terminal path
"""

